WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.472 --> 00:00:03.939
The plan pillar entails setting strategic priorities

2
00:00:03.939 --> 00:00:05.591
for the supply chain to ensure

3
00:00:05.591 --> 00:00:08.300
it can effectively understand and balance

4
00:00:08.300 --> 00:00:12.739
VHA enterprise needs against existing capabilities.

5
00:00:12.739 --> 00:00:14.744
Both clinical needs identification

6
00:00:14.744 --> 00:00:16.856
and requirements definition,

7
00:00:16.856 --> 00:00:18.968
including service level definition,

8
00:00:18.968 --> 00:00:20.525
occur at this stage,

9
00:00:20.525 --> 00:00:23.147
as do budgeting and financial planning.

10
00:00:23.147 --> 00:00:25.900
Where resource gaps exist, plans are crafted

11
00:00:25.900 --> 00:00:28.045
to address these gaps.

12
00:00:28.045 --> 00:00:30.818
Clear delineation of roles, responsibilities

13
00:00:30.818 --> 00:00:33.261
and cross-functional linkages are critical

14
00:00:33.261 --> 00:00:37.347
to fostering close collaboration and seamless execution.

15
00:00:37.347 --> 00:00:39.232
Plan as an independent pillar

16
00:00:39.232 --> 00:00:42.155
but also occurs within each of the other pillars.

